trans-unit.source: Represents a range of dates in a <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Calendar"></xref>.

CalendarDateRange objects are primarily used by the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.CalendarBlackoutDatesCollection> to specify a range of dates that are not selectable in a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar>.
trans-unit.target: CalendarDateRange objektumok elsősorban a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.CalendarBlackoutDatesCollection>megadásához, amelyek nem választható a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar> dátumtartomány</xref:System.Windows.Controls.CalendarBlackoutDatesCollection> által használt
